highlights.text: Olivia Rodrigo has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “good 4 u” is the highest at #5.
“Bilmem Mi?” by Sefo is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 122 spots at #75.
“Rumors (feat. Cardi B)” by Lizzo and Cardi B is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #21.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 237 weeks straight.
